        "body": "# DSA Questions Collection for Hacktoberfest 2025\r\n\r\nThis repository contains 40 curated DSA questions with solutions and links to their corresponding LeetCode problems. These questions are great for practice, interview preparation, and Hacktoberfest contributions.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTable of Contents\r\n1. [Question 1](#question-1)\r\n2. [Question 2](#question-2)\r\n3. [Question 3](#question-3)\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n Questions\r\n\r\nQuestion 1: [QUESTION NAME]\r\n**Problem Statement:**  \r\nFULL QUESTION\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\npython\r\n\r\nSOLUTION\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n✅ **Benefits of this format:**\r\n1. Clean headings make it easy to navigate.\r\n2. Problem statement is clearly separated from the solution.\r\n3. Code is highlighted with Markdown for readability.\r\n4. LeetCode links are clickable.\r\n5. Table of contents helps reviewers quickly jump to any question.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
